room_title: Escape room "The House in the Woods" by Paradox Escape Rooms in Valparaiso
review: Super fun game. We will be back! The owners are fantastic and the game made sense. Puzzle flow was good and decor fit. Highly recommend!

room_title: Escape room "The House in the Woods" by Paradox Escape Rooms in Valparaiso
